                            h4 Recharge!

                            p So take a break, take a nap, and recharge your batteries.  Work whatever hours you need (if it’s possible) and try to mimic normalcy.  Fake it till you make it!  Hopefully, these new tips and tricks can help you get through these tough times.  It worked for me and I’m still here, on lockdown, in Brooklyn.

